lead_paragraph: David Fletcher and Gregorio Petit hit two-run singles in the eighth inning, and the Los Angeles Angels rallied for a 6-4 victory over the Chicago Cubs on Sunday in the major leagues' final spring training game.

headline.print_headline: Angels Beats Cubs in Final Spring Training Game
